data.description: Gorgeous 2 Story Home with Open Concept, features 5 BR 3.5 Baths with plenty of  interior space and land sitting on 1.3 Acres. Freshly painted walls & gleaming hardwood floors throughout. Spacious  Kitchen and Dining Room area with island, stainless steel appliances, built in desk & wine rack. 9 ft. tray ceilings, Huge Master Ensuite with walk-in closet, double vanity and whirlpool jacuzzi style tub.  Large rear deck with plenty of room for entertaining, storage shed with power, as well as a large 2 -Car Garage. This unique home also comes with an exterior wood stove furnace to be used as a back-up or main heat source!
